<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/rachel-blake> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Rachel Blake MP was appointed as Parliamentary Secretary (Economic Secretary to the Treasury) in HM Treasury on 14 May 2026. She was elected as the MP for Cities of London and Westminster in July 2024."@en .
